Strzałkowo  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Łukta, within Ostróda County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-west of Łukta,  north-east of Ostróda, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
